e>roslaunch atlas_utils atlas_no_controllers.launch</code></p>\n<p>2) Uncheck enable physics</p>\n<p>3) run joint_animation.py from the <a data-is-external-link=\"true\" href=\"http://gazebosim.org/wiki/Tutorials/drcsim/2.0/ros_animated_robot\" rel=\"nofollow\">ros animated tutorial</a> and wait for the animation to be over</p>\n<p>4) robot then falls, which should not happen</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": null, "state": "resolved", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2013-02-01T02:33:48.790145+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2013-02-01T03:30:15.768380+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 113}